properties.summary: Time series of Air temperature observations from the Norwegian weather station Gullingen  (WIGOS ID 0-578-0-46220, station ID 46220). The observations have been through the data collection system of the Norwegian Meteorological institute which includes a number of automated and manual quality control routines. The number of available quality control routines is element dependent.
